- choose via-c3-improved
- use custom kernel config
- make sure libddmpeg is built

includes
- 2.4.24 -epia patch
- libdmpeg
- via-dri driver for X
- updated via driver for X
- optimization for i686 without cmov (patched gcc/glibc)

